docs {
  ## Submit Aggregate And Proofs

  Publish multiple signed aggregate and proofs to the beacon node. The beacon node will validate and broadcast them to the network.

  ### Request Body
  Array of signed aggregate and proof objects, each containing:
  - `message`: The aggregate and proof with `aggregator_index`, `aggregate` (attestation), and `selection_proof`
  - `signature`: BLS signature over the aggregate and proof message

  ### Response (200)
  Aggregate and proofs are stored and broadcast to the network. Returns 200 on success.
}
